              finished,
              timestamp,
              jobset_id,
              job,
              nixname,
              drvPath,
              system,
              isCachedBuild,
              fodCheck

              0,
              $1,
              $2,
              $3,
              $4,
              $5,
              $6,
              0,
              true
            ) RETURNING id;
